data.description: Motivated Seller!  Welcome to Ortonville Village!  Walking distance to the business district, library and park.  This home sits on beautiful lot with only Open Land behind you.  Enjoy summer evenings sitting around the paver fire pit making S'mores while the kids splash around in the above ground pool.  The large fire lit family room has direct access to the backyard. Kitchen has a granite island, all kitchen appliances stay with the home.  Some Updates include, 2020 40K three bucket Engineered Septic Field and new sod laid in backyard, New EF Furnace & AC 2021.  Lots of room in this 4 bedroom, two full baths home.  First floor bath has washer and dryer hookup and second floor bath has a two year old Jetted Tub.
